data.description: Move-in-ready 4-bedroom home in Nestor. Owner has put over $100k of recent upgrades in to include turf, new windows, fresh paint inside & out, mini split AC, new roof, extra bonus building/shed & much more! Large ~7,500 SF lot with new oversized driveway, extended yard/patio & low-maintenance landscaping. Home has 7.67 kW solar system w/ assumable Power Purchase Agreement currently at $178/month (right now only ~$0.17/kWh versus San Diego average of $0.39/kWh) Central location—close to regional park w/ over 22 miles of trails, Navy Bases, Imperial Beach, border crossing, shopping & more! Several producing fruit trees including dragonfruit, lemon, pink guava, blood oranges & Loquats. Get creative with bonus room–already decked out w/ electrical, insulation, plumbing & AC! Large lot in City of San Diego offers possibilities for ADUs w/ bonus program.
